description: Songs to listen to if you love and/or hate L.A. UPDATE (07/20/22): Dang, almost exactly 4 years later, over 1,000 users have since liked this playlist I started for a coworker who was moving out of LA. I hope you all are still enjoying this playlist and the slow drip of additions.
